# Per-dev / transient state the vendored scripts write ALONGSIDE themselves
# (SCRIPT_DIR = this dir): tunnel.sh's rendezvous moniker and any stray overlay
# pin manifest. Ignored so they can't be committed OR swept into `npm pack`
# (package.json `files` globs this whole dir). The vendored scripts + this
# .gitignore itself still ship.
.vms-moniker
*.tsv
